{
  "id": "soushenji-song-dingbo",
  "title": "宋定伯卖鬼",
  "titleEn": "Song Dingbo Sells a Ghost",
  "description": "A clever young man tricks a ghost and sells it at the market. FromErta Sou Shen Ji (4th century supernatural tales).",
  "source": "搜神记",
  "sourceEn": "In Search of the Supernatural",
  "difficulty": "HSK 3",
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "s01",
      "text": "很久以前，有一个年轻人叫宋定伯。",
      "pinyin": "Hěn jiǔ yǐqián, yǒu yí gè niánqīng rén jiào Sòng Dìngbó.",
      "translation": "Long ago, there was a young man named Song Dingbo.",
